    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2162604532" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2162604532" />
    <a title="Louis Muñoz" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4089459-louis-mu-oz"><img alt="Louis Muñoz" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1626029437p2/4089459.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2162604532?book_show_action=true">Oct 24, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Louis Muñoz" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Louis Muñoz" href="/user/show/4089459-louis-mu-oz">Louis Muñoz</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2162604532" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11823922279888217813">It&apos;s been some twenty years since I read this book, a book that has &quot;stayed&quot; with me in a very powerful way. In fact, I would say that &quot;Life and Death in Shanghai&quot; is among my Top Twenty among the hundreds of non-fiction books I have read. </span>
  <span id="freeText11823922279888217813" style="display:none">It's been some twenty years since I read this book, a book that has "stayed" with me in a very powerful way. In fact, I would say that "Life and Death in Shanghai" is among my Top Twenty among the hundreds of non-fiction books I have read. </span>
  <a data-text-id="11823922279888217813" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


