        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1364894134" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13715688995692497763">Amazing, eye-opening book that details what life was like in China during the Cultural Revolution.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review1364894134">
  <td colspan="2">
    <div class="updateActionLinks">
        <a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link1364894134" title="Flag this review as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=1364894134&amp;resource_type=Review&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F537404.Life_and_Death_in_Shanghai">flag</a>





      <span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_review_1364894134'><a id="like_count_review_1364894134" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1364894134?resource_type=Review"><span class="likesCount">12 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it gr-button gr-button--small" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F537404.Life_and_Death_in_Shanghai">Like</a></span>
